timetraCflowdMIBModule.description: This document is the SNMP MIB module to manage and provision the Alcatel Cflowd traffic flow analysis utility. Copyright 2003-2011 Alcatel-Lucent. TmnxCflowdAggScheme.name: TmnxCflowdAggScheme
TmnxCflowdAggScheme.description: The value of TmnxCflowdAggScheme is a bit mask which specifies the aggregation scheme(s) used to aggregate multiple individual flows into an aggregated flow for export to a remote host collector. If no aggregation scheme is specified, {}, no data will be exported to a remote collector host. If the 'raw (5)' scheme is specified, flow data is exported without aggregation in version 5 format. All other aggregation types use version 8 format to export the flow data to this remote host collector.

TmnxCflowdTemplateSet.name: TmnxCflowdTemplateSet
TmnxCflowdTemplateSet.description: The value of TmnxCflowdTemplateSet specifies the set of templates sent to the collector when using cflowd version 9 or 10. The recognized template-sets are: notApplicable (0) -- No cflowd packets will be sent to the collector basic (1) -- Basic flow data is sent. mplsIp (2) -- Extended flow data is sent that includes IP and MPLS information.

tmnxCflowdStatus.name: tmnxCflowdStatus
tmnxCflowdStatus.description: The desired state for Cflowd on this virtual router. An attempt to set tmnxCflowdStatus to 'delete' will fail if the Cflowd protocol is not in the administrative outOfService state, i.e. tmnxCflowdAdminStatus must first be set to 'outOfService'.

tmnxCflowdActiveTimeout.name: tmnxCflowdActiveTimeout
tmnxCflowdActiveTimeout.description: The value of tmnxCflowdActiveTimeout specifies the maximum amount of time, in minutes, before an active flow will be exported. If an individual flow is active for this amount of time, the flow is exported and a new flow is created.

tmnxCflowdInactiveTimeout.name: tmnxCflowdInactiveTimeout
tmnxCflowdInactiveTimeout.description: The value of tmnxCflowdInactiveTimeout specifies the amount of time, in seconds, that must elapse without a packet matching a flow before the flow is considered inactive.

tmnxCflowdCacheSize.name: tmnxCflowdCacheSize
tmnxCflowdCacheSize.description: The value of tmnxCflowdCacheSize specifies the maximum number of active flows to be maintained in the flow cache table.

tmnxCflowdSampleRate.name: tmnxCflowdSampleRate
tmnxCflowdSampleRate.description: The value of tmnxCflowdSampleRate specifies the rate at which traffic is sampled and forwarded for Cflowd analysis. A value of one (1) causes all packets to be analyzed. The default value '1000' causes every 1000th packet to be analyzed.

tmnxCflowdOverflow.name: tmnxCflowdOverflow
tmnxCflowdOverflow.description: The value of tmnxCflowdOverflow specifies the percentage number of flows to be flushed when the flow cache size has been exceeded.

tmnxCflowdAdminStatus.name: tmnxCflowdAdminStatus
tmnxCflowdAdminStatus.description: The value of tmnxCflowdAdminStatus indicates the desired administrative state for the Cflowd data analysis.

tmnxCflowdOperStatus.name: tmnxCflowdOperStatus
tmnxCflowdOperStatus.description: The value of tmnxCflowdOperStatus indicates the current operational status of the Cflowd data analysis.

tmnxCflowdActiveFlows.name: tmnxCflowdActiveFlows
tmnxCflowdActiveFlows.description: The value of tmnxCflowdActiveFlows is a gauge that indicates the current number of active flows being collected.

tmnxCflowdAggregation.name: tmnxCflowdAggregation
tmnxCflowdAggregation.description: The value of tmnxCflowdAggregation is a bit mask which specifies the aggregation scheme(s) currently used to aggregate multiple individual flows into an aggregated flow for export to one or more remote host collectors configured in the tmnxCFHostTable. If no aggregation scheme is specified, {}, no data will be exported. If the 'raw (5)' scheme is specified, flow data is exported without aggregation in version 5 format. All other aggregation types use version 8 format to export the flow data to the remote host collector.

tmnxCFHostTableLastChanged.name: tmnxCFHostTableLastChanged
tmnxCFHostTableLastChanged.description: timestamp of last change to tmnxCFHostTable.

tmnxCflowdMaxCollectors.name: tmnxCflowdMaxCollectors
tmnxCflowdMaxCollectors.description: The value of tmnxCflowdMaxCollectors specifies the maximum number of row entries that can be created in the tmnxCFHostTable.

tmnxCflowdTotalPktsRcvd.name: tmnxCflowdTotalPktsRcvd
tmnxCflowdTotalPktsRcvd.description: The value of tmnxCflowdTotalPktsRcvd indicates the total number of packets received for Cflowd.

tmnxCflowdTotalPktsDropped.name: tmnxCflowdTotalPktsDropped
tmnxCflowdTotalPktsDropped.description: The value of tmnxCflowdTotalPktsDropped indicates the total number of packets dropped for Cflowd.

tmnxCflowdTemplateRetransmit.name: tmnxCflowdTemplateRetransmit
tmnxCflowdTemplateRetransmit.description: The value of tmnxCflowdTemplateRetransmit specifies the period of time, in seconds, for a template to be retransmitted.

tmnxCflowdGenRawFlowsCreated.name: tmnxCflowdGenRawFlowsCreated
tmnxCflowdGenRawFlowsCreated.description: The value of tmnxCflowdGenRawFlowsCreated indicates the number of raw flows created by system.

tmnxCflowdGenAggrFlowsCreated.name: tmnxCflowdGenAggrFlowsCreated
tmnxCflowdGenAggrFlowsCreated.description: The value of tmnxCflowdGenAggrFlowsCreated indicates the number of aggregate flows created by system.

tmnxCflowdGenRawFlowsMatched.name: tmnxCflowdGenRawFlowsMatched
tmnxCflowdGenRawFlowsMatched.description: The value of tmnxCflowdGenRawFlowsMatched indicates the number of raw patckets matched to an existing raw flow.

tmnxCflowdGenAggrFlowsMatched.name: tmnxCflowdGenAggrFlowsMatched
tmnxCflowdGenAggrFlowsMatched.description: The value of tmnxCflowdGenAggrFlowsMatched indicates the number of packets matched to an existing aggregate flow.

tmnxCflowdGenRawFlowsFlushed.name: tmnxCflowdGenRawFlowsFlushed
tmnxCflowdGenRawFlowsFlushed.description: The value of tmnxCflowdGenRawFlowsFlushed indicates the number of raw flows flushed.

tmnxCflowdGenAggrFlowsFlushed.name: tmnxCflowdGenAggrFlowsFlushed
tmnxCflowdGenAggrFlowsFlushed.description: The value of tmnxCflowdGenAggrFlowsMatched indicates the number of aggregate flows flushed.

tmnxCflowdGenOverflowEvents.name: tmnxCflowdGenOverflowEvents
tmnxCflowdGenOverflowEvents.description: The value of tmnxCflowdGenOverflowEvents indicates the number of times the flow cache has entered the overflow state.

tmnxCflowdGenDroppedFlows.name: tmnxCflowdGenDroppedFlows
tmnxCflowdGenDroppedFlows.description: The value of tmnxCflowdGenDroppedFlows indicates the number of times a flow was dropped. Data from dropped flows are not reported to any collector.

tmnxCFHostTable.name: tmnxCFHostTable
tmnxCFHostTable.description: A table of all Cflowd remote collector host definitions.

tmnxCFHostEntry.name: tmnxCFHostEntry
tmnxCFHostEntry.description: Information about a particular Cflowd remote collector host entry. Entries in the tmnxCFHostTable are created and destroyed via SNMP Set requests to tmnxCFHostRowStatus. There is no StorageType object, entries have a presumed StorageType of 'nonVolatile'.

tmnxCFHostAddress.name: tmnxCFHostAddress
tmnxCFHostAddress.description: The value of tmnxCFHostAddress specifies the IP address of a remote Cflowd collector host to receive the exported Cflowd data.

tmnxCFHostUdpPort.name: tmnxCFHostUdpPort
tmnxCFHostUdpPort.description: The value of tmnxCFHostUdpPort specifies the UDP port number on the remote Cflowd collector host to receive the exported Cflowd data.

tmnxCFHostRowStatus.name: tmnxCFHostRowStatus
tmnxCFHostRowStatus.description: Row entries in this table are created and destroyed via SNMP set requests. A row cannot be destroyed if the value of tmnxCFHostAdminStatus is not 'outOfService'.

tmnxCFHostEntryLastChanged.name: tmnxCFHostEntryLastChanged
tmnxCFHostEntryLastChanged.description: The value of tmnxCFHostEntryLastChanged is the sysUpTime when this row entry was last changed.

tmnxCFHostDescription.name: tmnxCFHostDescription
tmnxCFHostDescription.description: The value of tmnxCFHostDescription is a user provided description string for this Cflowd remote collector host. It can consist of any printable, seven-bit ASCII characters up to 80 characters in length.

tmnxCFHostAdminStatus.name: tmnxCFHostAdminStatus
tmnxCFHostAdminStatus.description: The value of tmnxCFHostAdminStatus indicates the desired administrative state for this Cflowd remote collector host.

tmnxCFHostOperStatus.name: tmnxCFHostOperStatus
tmnxCFHostOperStatus.description: The value of tmnxCFHostOperStatus indicates the current operational status of this Cflowd remote collector host.

tmnxCFHostASType.name: tmnxCFHostASType
tmnxCFHostASType.description: The value of tmnxCFHostASType specifies which style of AS reporting is used in the exported flow data. An AS type of 'origin' reflects the endpoints of the AS path which the flow is following. An AS type of 'peer' reflects the AS of the previous and next hops for the flow.

tmnxCFHostAggregation.name: tmnxCFHostAggregation
tmnxCFHostAggregation.description: The value of tmnxCFHostAggregation is a bit mask which specifies the aggregation scheme(s) used to aggregate multiple individual flows into an aggregated flow for export to this remote host collector. If no aggregation scheme is specified, {}, no data will be exported for this remote collector host. If the 'raw (5)' scheme is specified, flow data is exported without aggregation in version 5 format. All other aggregation types use version 8 format to export the flow data to this remote host collector.

tmnxCFHostRecordsSent.name: tmnxCFHostRecordsSent
tmnxCFHostRecordsSent.description: The value of tmnxCFHostRecordsSent is the number of Cflowd records that have been transmitted to this remote collector host. This object is only applicable for a remote collector host with tmnxCFHostVersion set to either 5, 8 or 10.

tmnxCFHostLastPktSent.name: tmnxCFHostLastPktSent
tmnxCFHostLastPktSent.description: The value of tmnxCFHostLastPktSent is the sysUpTime when the last Cflowd packet was sent to this remote collector host.

tmnxCFHostVersion.name: tmnxCFHostVersion
tmnxCFHostVersion.description: The value of tmnxCFHostVersion specifies the version of this remote collector host. The following table indicates which objects are either limited, or not supported for a particular version: Version Object Restrictions -------- ----------------------- --------------- 5 tmnxCFHostAggregation not supported tmnxCFHostTemplateSet not supported tmnxCFHostPacketsSent use tmnxCFHostRecordsSent 8 tmnxCFHostTemplateSet not supported tmnxCFHostPacketsSent use tmnxCFHostRecordsSent 9 tmnxCFHostASType not supported tmnxCFHostAggregation not supported tmnxCFHostRecordsSent use tmnxCFHostPacketsSent 10 tmnxCFHostASType not supported tmnxCFHostAggregation not supported tmnxCFHostPacketsSent use tmnxCFHostRecordsSent

tmnxCFHostTemplateSet.name: tmnxCFHostTemplateSet
tmnxCFHostTemplateSet.description: The value of tmnxCFHostTemplateSet specifies the template-set used by this remote collector host. If the tmnxCFHostVersion is not set to the version 9 or 10, the tmnxCFHostTemplateSet is limited to 'notApplicable(0)'. When the tmnxCFHostVersion is set to version 9 or 10 the tmnxCFHostTemplateSet is defaulted to 'basic (1)'.

tmnxCFHostPacketsSent.name: tmnxCFHostPacketsSent
tmnxCFHostPacketsSent.description: The value of tmnxCFHostPacketsSent is the number of Cflowd packets that have been transmitted to this remote collector host. This object is only applicable for a remote collector host with tmnxCFHostVersion set to 9.

tmnxCflowdVersionStatsTable.name: tmnxCflowdVersionStatsTable
tmnxCflowdVersionStatsTable.description: The tmnxCflowdVersionStatsTable consists of the overall statistics based on collector version.

tmnxCflowdVersionStatsEntry.name: tmnxCflowdVersionStatsEntry
tmnxCflowdVersionStatsEntry.description: The tmnxCflowdVersionStatsEntry contains the information pertaining to the system wide statistics for the specified version index.

tmnxCflowdVersionIndex.name: tmnxCflowdVersionIndex
tmnxCflowdVersionIndex.description: The value of tmnxCflowdVersionIndex specifies the row in the tmnxCflowdVersionStatsTable that pertains to the cflowd collector version.

tmnxCflowdVersionStatus.name: tmnxCflowdVersionStatus
tmnxCflowdVersionStatus.description: The value of tmnxCflowdVersionStatus indicates whether or not the version is in use in the system.

tmnxCflowdVersionSent.name: tmnxCflowdVersionSent
tmnxCflowdVersionSent.description: The value of tmnxCflowdVersionSent indicates the number of packets transmitted for the specified version.

tmnxCflowdVersionOpen.name: tmnxCflowdVersionOpen
tmnxCflowdVersionOpen.description: The value of tmnxCflowdVersionOpen indicates the number of open packets pending for the specified version.

tmnxCflowdVersionErrors.name: tmnxCflowdVersionErrors
tmnxCflowdVersionErrors.description: The value of tmnxCflowdVersionErrors indicates the number of errored packets for the specified version.

tmnxCflowdV5StatsTable.name: tmnxCflowdV5StatsTable
tmnxCflowdV5StatsTable.description: The tmnxCflowdV5StatsTable consists of the version 5 statistics for a particular remote collector host.

tmnxCflowdV5StatsEntry.name: tmnxCflowdV5StatsEntry
tmnxCflowdV5StatsEntry.description: The tmnxCflowdV5StatsEntry contains the statistics information pertaining to the specified remote collector host.

tmnxCflowdV5Sent.name: tmnxCflowdV5Sent
tmnxCflowdV5Sent.description: The value of tmnxCflowdV5Sent indicates the number of packets transmitted for the specified remote collector host.

tmnxCflowdV5Open.name: tmnxCflowdV5Open
tmnxCflowdV5Open.description: The value of tmnxCflowdV5Open indicates the number of open packets pending for the specified remote collector host.

tmnxCflowdV5Errors.name: tmnxCflowdV5Errors
tmnxCflowdV5Errors.description: The value of tmnxCflowdV5Errors indicates the number of errored packets for the specified remote collector host.

tmnxCflowdAggregationStatsTable.name: tmnxCflowdAggregationStatsTable
tmnxCflowdAggregationStatsTable.description: The tmnxCflowdAggregationStatsTable consists of the overall statistics based on aggregation type.

tmnxCflowdAggregationStatsEntry.name: tmnxCflowdAggregationStatsEntry
tmnxCflowdAggregationStatsEntry.description: The tmnxCflowdAggregationStatsEntry contains the information pertaining to the remote collector host statistics for the specified aggregation index.

tmnxCflowdAggregationIndex.name: tmnxCflowdAggregationIndex
tmnxCflowdAggregationIndex.description: The value of tmnxCflowdAggregationIndex specifies the row in the tmnxCflowdAggregationStatsTable that pertains to the cflowd collector aggregation type.

tmnxCflowdAggregationStatus.name: tmnxCflowdAggregationStatus
tmnxCflowdAggregationStatus.description: The value of tmnxCflowdAggregationStatus indicates whether or not the aggregation is in use in the remote collector host entry.

tmnxCflowdAggregationSent.name: tmnxCflowdAggregationSent
tmnxCflowdAggregationSent.description: The value of tmnxCflowdAggregationSent indicates the number of packets transmitted for the specified aggregation type.

tmnxCflowdAggregationOpen.name: tmnxCflowdAggregationOpen
tmnxCflowdAggregationOpen.description: The value of tmnxCflowdAggregationOpen indicates the number of open packets pending for the specified aggregation type.

tmnxCflowdAggregationErrors.name: tmnxCflowdAggregationErrors
tmnxCflowdAggregationErrors.description: The value of tmnxCflowdAggregationErrors indicates the number of errored packets for the specified aggregation type.

tmnxCflowdTemplateStatsTable.name: tmnxCflowdTemplateStatsTable
tmnxCflowdTemplateStatsTable.description: The tmnxCflowdTemplateStatsTable consists of the overall statistics based on template flows for a specified remote collector host entry.

tmnxCflowdTemplateStatsEntry.name: tmnxCflowdTemplateStatsEntry
tmnxCflowdTemplateStatsEntry.description: The tmnxCflowdTemplateStatsEntry contains the information pertaining to the remote collector host statistics for the specified template index.

tmnxCflowdTemplateFlowIndex.name: tmnxCflowdTemplateFlowIndex
tmnxCflowdTemplateFlowIndex.description: The value of tmnxCflowdTemplateFlowIndex specifies the row in the tmnxCflowdTemplateStatsTable that pertains to the cflowd collector Template type.

tmnxCflowdTemplateLastTxTime.name: tmnxCflowdTemplateLastTxTime
tmnxCflowdTemplateLastTxTime.description: The value of tmnxCflowdTemplateLastTxTime indicates the time, since system startup, when the specified template was last transmitted.

tmnxCflowdTemplateSent.name: tmnxCflowdTemplateSent
tmnxCflowdTemplateSent.description: The value of tmnxCflowdTemplateSent indicates the number of packets transmitted for the specified Template type.

tmnxCflowdTemplateOpen.name: tmnxCflowdTemplateOpen
tmnxCflowdTemplateOpen.description: The value of tmnxCflowdTemplateOpen indicates the number of open packets pending for the specified Template type.

tmnxCflowdTemplateErrors.name: tmnxCflowdTemplateErrors
tmnxCflowdTemplateErrors.description: The value of tmnxCflowdTemplateErrors indicates the number of errored packets for the specified Template type.

tmnxCflowdFlowFailureReasonCode.name: tmnxCflowdFlowFailureReasonCode
tmnxCflowdFlowFailureReasonCode.description: Used by tmnxCflowdFlowCreateFailure and tmnxCflowdFlowFlushFailure to report the failure reason code.

tmnxCflowdFlowUnsuppIPProtoNum.name: tmnxCflowdFlowUnsuppIPProtoNum
tmnxCflowdFlowUnsuppIPProtoNum.description: tmnxCflowdFlowUnsuppIPProtoNum is used to specify the unsupported IP protocol for the tmnxCflowdFlowUnsuppProto event. This object was made obsolete in 7x50 SR Release 8.0.

tmnxCflowdCreated.name: tmnxCflowdCreated
tmnxCflowdCreated.description: The tmnxCflowdCreated event is generated when Cflowd instance is created on the system. This notification was made obsolete in 7x50 SR Release 8.0.

tmnxCflowdCreateFailure.name: tmnxCflowdCreateFailure
tmnxCflowdCreateFailure.description: The tmnxCflowdCreateFailure event is generated when Cflowd instance creation fails on the system.

tmnxCflowdDeleted.name: tmnxCflowdDeleted
tmnxCflowdDeleted.description: The tmnxCflowdDeleted event is generated when Cflowd instance is removed from the system. This notification was made obsolete in 7x50 SR Release 8.0.

tmnxCflowdStateChange.name: tmnxCflowdStateChange
tmnxCflowdStateChange.description: The tmnxCflowdStateChange event is triggered when tmnxCflowdAdminStatus or tmnxCflowdOperStatus reports a change.

tmnxCflowdCleared.name: tmnxCflowdCleared
tmnxCflowdCleared.description: The tmnxCflowdCleared event is triggered when the Cflowd statistics are cleared. This notification was made obsolete in 7x50 SR Release 8.0.

tmnxCflowdFlowCreateFailure.name: tmnxCflowdFlowCreateFailure
tmnxCflowdFlowCreateFailure.description: The tmnxCflowdFlowCreateFailure event is generated when the creation of a Cflowd flow fails.

tmnxCflowdFlowFlushFailure.name: tmnxCflowdFlowFlushFailure
tmnxCflowdFlowFlushFailure.description: The tmnxCflowdFlowFlushFailure event is generated when the flushing of a Cflowd flow fails. This notification was made obsolete in 7x50 SR Release 8.0. It was replaced by tmnxCflowdPacketTxFailure.

tmnxCflowdFlowUnsuppProto.name: tmnxCflowdFlowUnsuppProto
tmnxCflowdFlowUnsuppProto.description: The tmnxCflowdFlowUnsuppProto event is generated in case of an unsupported IP protocol. This notification was made obsolete in 7x50 SR Release 8.0.

tmnxCflowdPacketTxFailure.name: tmnxCflowdPacketTxFailure
tmnxCflowdPacketTxFailure.description: The tmnxCflowdPacketTxFailure event is generated when a cflowd packet fails to transmit from an active collector host.

tmnxCflowdCompliance.name: tmnxCflowdCompliance
tmnxCflowdCompliance.description: The compliance statement for revision 2.0 of TIMETRA-CFLOWD-MIB.

tmnxCflowdComplianceV6v0.name: tmnxCflowdComplianceV6v0
tmnxCflowdComplianceV6v0.description: The compliance statement of TIMETRA-CFLOWD-MIB for release 6.0.

tmnxCflowdComplianceV8v0.name: tmnxCflowdComplianceV8v0
tmnxCflowdComplianceV8v0.description: The compliance statement of TIMETRA-CFLOWD-MIB for release 8.0.

tmnxCflowdComplianceV10v0.name: tmnxCflowdComplianceV10v0
tmnxCflowdComplianceV10v0.description: The compliance statement of TIMETRA-CFLOWD-MIB for release 10.0.

tmnxCflowdGlobalGroup.name: tmnxCflowdGlobalGroup
tmnxCflowdGlobalGroup.description: The group of objects supporting management of Cflowd general capabilities on Alcatel 7x50 SR series systems.

tmnxCflowdHostGroup.name: tmnxCflowdHostGroup
tmnxCflowdHostGroup.description: The group of objects supporting management of Cflowd hosts on Alcatel 7x50 SR series systems.

tmnxCflowdNotifyObjsGroup.name: tmnxCflowdNotifyObjsGroup
tmnxCflowdNotifyObjsGroup.description: The group of objects supporting Cflowd notifications on Alcatel 7x50 SR series systems.

tmnxCflowdNotificationGroup.name: tmnxCflowdNotificationGroup
tmnxCflowdNotificationGroup.description: The group of notifications supporting the Cflowd feature on Alcatel 7x50 SR series systems.

tmnxCflowdGlobalGroupV6v0.name: tmnxCflowdGlobalGroupV6v0
tmnxCflowdGlobalGroupV6v0.description: The group of objects supporting management of Cflowd general capabilities on Alcatel 7xx0 SR series systems for release 6.0.

tmnxCflowdObsoleteV8v0Group.name: tmnxCflowdObsoleteV8v0Group
tmnxCflowdObsoleteV8v0Group.description: The group of objects that were made obsolete On Alcatel 7xx0 SR series systems for release 8.0.

tmnxCflowdGroupV8v0.name: tmnxCflowdGroupV8v0
tmnxCflowdGroupV8v0.description: The group of objects added in release 8.0 to support management of Cflowd capabilities on Alcatel 7xx0 SR series systems.

tmnxCflowdNotifyObjsV8v0Group.name: tmnxCflowdNotifyObjsV8v0Group
tmnxCflowdNotifyObjsV8v0Group.description: The group of objects supporting Cflowd notifications on Alcatel 7x50 SR series systems.

tmnxCflowdNotificationV8v0Group.name: tmnxCflowdNotificationV8v0Group
tmnxCflowdNotificationV8v0Group.description: The group of notifications supporting the Cflowd feature on Alcatel 7x50 SR series systems.

tmnxCflowdStatisticsV10v0Group.name: tmnxCflowdStatisticsV10v0Group
tmnxCflowdStatisticsV10v0Group.description: The group of objects enhancing Cflowd statistics on Alcatel 7x50 SR series systems in release 10.0.
